Description.SourceString: The positioning of your Heroes is important! Heroes in the front row protect the Heroes directly behind them. As long as the Hero in front is alive, the Hero behind them cannot be targeted by non-area of effect attacks.
Description.LocalizedString: The positioning of your Heroes is important! Heroes in the front row protect the Heroes directly behind them. As long as the Hero in front is alive, the Hero behind them cannot be targeted by non-area of effect attacks.
